narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: A good way to learn what other students in the department have been up to and to see what works and what doesn't work in terms of communicating one's work.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Structurally low-stakes class for participants and not the presenters so it's easy to mentally check out. It is good that there is a forum for students to have to present and get their work done well.
